2. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a likely category as the paper deals with a large dataset of images. 
3. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is another possible category as the paper evaluates the performance of algorithms in identifying and verifying individuals from a large dataset. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper discusses the impact of training data size on algorithm performance. 
5. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper discusses the security implications of face recognition technology.
